nodes.title: Workflow Information
widgets_values:
STRANGE DAYS v3

https://civitai.com/models/234473
https://openart.ai/workflows/akatsuzi/strange-days-gaussian-noise

This is a demo for using latent guassian noise in place of an empty latent image.

You can use it in three modes:
- Full workflow including Ultimate Upscale
- Preview workflow with Ultimate Upscale switched off
- Upscale recycled images from previews

Use the Fast Goups Muter nodes to switch on and off groups. There are some notes in the workflow for guidance.

You will probably need to download some custom nodes to run this. You can use Find Missing Nodes in ComfyUI Manager to fetch them.

Node packs you will need include:
- rgthree
- SD Advanced Noise
- Comfyroll Custom Nodes
- Ultimate SD Upscale

nodes.title: Recycle Mode
widgets_values:
To upscale a recycled image select:
Enable Inputs
Enable Upscale Recycled Image
Then drag your image into Load Image.

nodes.title: Preview Mode
widgets_values:
For preview mode, switch off:
Enable Upscale
Enable Upscale Recycled Image
